Ecopetrol Is Closer to Making ‘Big’ Oil Discovery, RCN Says

-- B y   A n d r e a   J a r a m i l l o
-- 
2011-08-26T13:32:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-26/ecopetrol-is-closer-to-making-big-oil-discovery-rcn-says.html
Ecopetrol SA (ECOPETL) ,  Colombia ’s largest oil
company, is getting “closer” to making a “big” oil
discovery,  RCN Radio  reported, citing Chief Executive Officer
 Javier Gutierrez .  This is a possibility as the company searches for new
reserves in Colombia,  Peru ,  Brazil  and the U.S. Gulf of  Mexico ,
Gutierrez told Bogota-based RCN in an interview. Ecopetrol’s
production will increase to about 1.3 million barrels a day in
2020, he has said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrea Jaramillo in Bogota at 
 ajaramillo1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dale Crofts at   dcrofts@bloomberg.net  